OL,4,Cafter 36 years
OL,6,FWatch as Kay Burley announces her
OL,7,Fretirement from Sky News after 36 years
OL,9,FBroadcaster Kay Burley is retiring
OL,10,Ffrom Sky News after 36 years.
OL,12,FShe made the surprise announcement on
OL,13,FWednesday morning at the end of her
OL,14,Fbreakfast programme, which was her
OL,15,Flast day on air with the broadcaster.
OL,17,FThe veteran journalist, 64, was one of
OL,18,Fthe original presenters who helped
OL,19,Flaunch Sky News in 1989, and she has
OL,20,Fpresented the morning slot since 2019.
