OL,3,CKay Burley steps down from Sky News
OL,4,Cafter 36 years
OL,6,FClosing her show, she said: "After
OL,7,Fover a million minutes of live TV
OL,8,Fnews, more than anyone else in the
OL,9,Fworld, it's time for me to indulge in
OL,10,Fsome of my other passions, including
OL,11,Fmy love for travel.
OL,13,F"So, after covering 12 separate
OL,14,Fgeneral elections, including Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer's victory last year, I am
OL,16,Fretiring from Sky News, let
OL,17,Fpoliticians of every party just
OL,18,Frejoice at that news."
