OL,6,FHer last day also coincided with Sky
OL,7,FNews's 36th birthday and she used her
OL,8,Ffinal moments to pay tribute to how it
OL,9,Fhad progressed from a "standing start
OL,10,Fto one of the most recognised and
OL,11,Fvalued brands in global news".
OL,13,FSpeaking to her viewers, she said:
OL,14,F"Thank you for waking up and tuning in
OL,15,Fevery morning. I can't tell you how
OL,16,Fmuch I have appreciated your support
OL,17,Fover the last three and a half decades
OL,18,F` you're awesome."
