OL,3,CKay Burley steps down from Sky News
OL,4,Cafter 36 years
OL,6,FRaised in Wigan, Lancashire, Burley
OL,7,Ftook her first steps into journalism
OL,8,Freporting for the Wigan Evening Post
OL,9,Fand Chronicle aged 17.
OL,11,FShe later secured a job with the BBC
OL,12,Fon its local radio stations and then
OL,13,FTyne Tees Television, before joining
OL,14,Fthe now defunct TV-am in 1985 as a
OL,15,Freporter and occasional newsreader.
OL,17,FBurley was recruited for the fledgling
OL,18,FSky News in 1989 as one of its
OL,19,Ffounding presenters.
