OL,6,FIn September 2018, the broadcaster was
OL,7,Fgiven her own show on Sky News, and a
OL,8,Fyear later she moved to the breakfast
OL,9,Ftime slot.
OL,11,FOver the years she has interviewed
OL,12,Ffigures including former prime
OL,13,Fminister Rishi Sunak and Ukrainian
OL,14,FPresident Volodymyr Zelensky.
