OL,3,CKay Burley steps down from Sky News
OL,4,Cafter 36 years
OL,6,FDuring the pandemic, she regularly
OL,7,Fgrilled politicians about lockdown
OL,8,Frules and questioned then Cabinet
OL,9,Fminister Michael Gove on the
OL,10,Fcontroversy over former No 10 adviser
OL,11,FDominic Cummings' trip to Barnard
OL,12,FCastle in May 2020.
OL,14,FBut in December 2020, Burley was
OL,15,Fsuspended from her role for six months
OL,16,Fafter an internal review found she
OL,17,Fbroke Covid-19 rules during
OL,18,Fcelebrations for her 60th birthday.
