OL,3,CKay Burley steps down from Sky News
OL,4,Cafter 36 years
OL,6,FBurley later apologised for her
OL,7,Factions, describing herself as an
OL,8,F"idiot" and agreeing that she was
OL,9,F"appropriately sanctioned" by the
OL,10,Fchannel.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, in October 2023, Sky News
OL,13,Fconceded that on-air remarks by Burley
OL,14,Fabout the Palestinian ambassador to
OL,15,Fthe UK, Dr Husam Zomlot, "gave a
OL,16,Fpotentially misleading representation"
OL,17,Fof his views after 1,537 complaints
OL,18,Fwere made to the media watchdog Ofcom
OL,19,Fabout the segment.
