OL,6,FFormer BBC Newsnight producer Sam
OL,7,FMcAlister, who secured the Newsnight
OL,8,Finterview with the Duke of York, said
OL,9,Fshe was "devastated" to hear Burley
OL,10,Fwas retiring, describing her as a
OL,11,F"total inspiration" to her as a single
OL,12,Fparent and woman from a different
OL,13,Fbackground.
OL,15,FIt comes as Sky News undertakes a
OL,16,Fmajor restructuring, moving away from
OL,17,FTV output towards digital media.
